Class Benefits

Our program for success focuses on your health and wellness while building a strong foundation for a longer life expectancy. Classes include all technical mechanics of lifts, a range of motion assessment & movement evaluation, barbell techniques, barbell safety, weightlifting etiquette, lifting practice, gym etiquette and basic skills followed by a practice workout in each class.
